&lt;/h3>&lt;ol>
&lt;li>Access to &lt;strong>Route 53&lt;/strong>, and select your domain&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Under &lt;strong>Records&lt;/strong>, click &lt;strong>Create record&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol>
