&lt;li>Price class: Select desired &lt;strong>regions&lt;/strong>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Alternate domain name: Add the &lt;strong>domain name&lt;/strong> configured previously&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
