&lt;h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>By integrating AWS S3, Route 53, CloudFront, and ACM, we successfully hosted a static web application with a robust and modern infrastructure. The website is not only highly available and securely accessible via HTTPS, but also globally distributed with low latency and reachable through a custom domain. This setup ensures a smooth and reliable user experience while taking full advantage of AWSâ€™s scalability, performance, and cost-effectiveness.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>